title: DDFP 402: Week 9 review & "Dear Ikey"
itunes:title: DDFP 402: Week 9 review & "Dear Ikey"
description:
Shek is joined by Ike Taylor and Maurice Jones-Drew to discuss the recent outbreak of sideline scuffles, debate the future of Blaine Gabbert and the 49ers and delve into how well players know the reputations of referees. Plus, Ike and MJD respond to relationship questions from A.J. Hawk, Dashon Goldson and Gerald McCoy in the newest edition of "Dear Ikey." 

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
